1  Make sure "Main Camera" exists in your scene
2. Create a scripts with filename "LineRendererCollider.cs" copy the content of LineRendererCollider.cs into it.
3. LineRendererCollider.s script uses the new input system, if you are on old one input manager, rmb to change two lines( code below have details ))
4. Create an Empty GameObject in your scene, and add the LineRendererCollider script as a component
5. click Play, you should be able to see a red line, click on it, will change color, then hooray, collider works
